Our Results
Y&S Accounting has helped several businesses and thousands of individuals to stay compliant with the ATO and to achieve their financial and business goals.

Our Mission
To provide superior quality accounting services for the wellbeing of the Latin American community in Australia.

Our Vision
To become Australia’s most trusted accountancy and business advisory service for Latin American immigrants. We aim to achieve our vision by embracing the following statements:
Equality of opportunities for people with a multicultural background.
Cloud accounting and automation are key to business success.
We believe starting and managing a business, should be simple and stress-free. Let’s work together

Our Team
Y&S Accounting is a company established since 2008, with the aim of providing accounting and tax services to individuals and businesses.
Yaritza Salazar
Founder and Director
Bio
Yaritza has more than 10 years of experience in the provision of financial/accounting services. She graduated from Bond University in 2004 with a bachelor of commerce majoring in accounting and completed her CPA in 2007.
The combined exposure to high net worth clients at various companies throughout her career, as well as individuals and businesses at her own practice has given her a very broad view of accounting and taxation matters.

Sebastian Garcia
Brisbane Manager
Bio
Sebastian provides a comprehensive range of professional accounting and business services to Y&S Accounting’s clients – all with the aim of helping them succeed in business. He has over 8 years of accounting experience between Argentina and Australia. Sebastian works with individuals and small to medium enterprises to structure their tax, accounts and finances to maximise financial and business outcomes and to adopt effective accounting software and systems.
